summary:
Marketing communication professional specialized in business marketing, with more than six years of experience in the development of brand identity and marketing strategies. With the capacity to create and implement strategic plans and advertising campaigns that favor the objectives of the brand. 
Passionate about the power of storytelling, bringing brands to life through design, insights, and media. Committed, with management skills and focus on results.
